# Property-based test auto-generated snapshots.
# Each `proptest!` case produces one Soroban test_snapshot file (default
# 256 cases per test). Unlike the deterministic fixed-fixture snapshots
# elsewhere in the repo, these are not regression-detection artifacts —
# random inputs imply non-reproducible filenames across runs. Excluded
# to keep the repo lean (12 property tests x 256 cases = ~3000 files).
crates/safe-oracle/test_snapshots/prop_*.json

